attributes.comment: As a 65-year-old Woman I have already been sexually assaulted in a clinical or emergency room setting three times since College the first two by men/male Physicians and the last time by a wild-eyed middle-aged woman MD and I am at the beginning of a lawsuit regarding Medicaid fraud which is rampant in the state of Oregon that supports the mutilation of children. If the federal Medicaid and Medicare program is contaminated with garbage language that disadvantages Women even more than we already are regarding healthcare there will be a glut of lawsuits costing the American people so I object to anything that deflects from the idea that Women are human and have sex based rights that we refuse to give up in order to shield perverted individuals claiming theirfeelings are more important than SCIENCE and Women and girls safety. Not on my watch.
